24 SECTION 1. Arkansas Code Title 6, Chapter 16, Subchapter 1, is amended
25 to add an additional section to read as follows:
26 6-16-163. Digital media standards — Required — Definitions.
27 (a) The General Assembly finds that:
28 (1) There is an urgent need to address the potentially harmful
29 effects of social media on children and adults; and
30 (2) It is crucial that the General Assembly establish a means by
31 which students in the State of Arkansas can learn to be digitally literate
32 and responsible in order to protect against the potentially harmful effects
33 of social media.
34 (b) As used in this section:
35 (1)(A) "Artificial intelligence" means a machine-based system
36 that can make decisions, recommendations, or predictions based on a set of
