5 (2) "Digital citizenship" means the application of the standards
6 of appropriate, responsible, and healthy online behavior, including the
7 ability to access, analyze, evaluate, create, and act on all forms of digital
8 communication;
9 (3) "Digital wellness" means the physical and emotional health
10 impacts of media use, with attention to the development of conscious,
